message.body: What's for dinner?
I made 2 home made pizzas, pizazz and regular with half ppperoni
Ok. Cause me and Michael were taking about maybe getting nachos tonight. But pizza is good. Maybe we can do both if we want.
I'm going to try to leave early. I didn't have parents today. I'm just doing a wound competency online right now and want to try to leave when I'm done.
Ok. Is michael meeting you after work or is dad getting you?
Don't know. He didn't say.
If your done soon are u just walking home?
Yeah
Ok. Let me know when you're leaving.
Yup
Never left me info! Flight number, seat number,etc, for both flights! Call me!
On the plane now. Waiting to take off.
Ok. Call me when u land. Love you!
Yup. Love you.
The flight was delayed. Be there in 20 minutes.
Just landed.
Call me when you deplane! Love you!
Call me! You should have been there by now. Are u ok?
We are not there yet. I said I will call you when we are there.
Just getting worried. It's been an hour since you landed
We're here.
Ok. Love you! Sorry to be a pain in the ass but i love and i worry. Text me later and let me know your alive.lol
